# Cloudflare Workers Static Assets _redirects (same format as Pages).
#
# /check -> the AEO scanner. Cold outreach emails link to the
# 2-label apex (neverranked.com/check?url=...&utm_*) instead of the
# 3-label check.neverranked.com, because SpamAssassin's URI_TRY_3LD
# penalizes a 3-label "try this" hostname by ~2 points (measured:
# the single biggest content deduction, mail-tester 7/10). The
# original query string (?url= + every utm_*) is preserved on the
# redirect, so the recipient lands on the real scanner with UTM
# attribution intact and the spam filter only sees the clean 2LD.
/check      https://check.neverranked.com/          302
/check/*    https://check.neverranked.com/:splat    302
